---
// src/components/About.astro - Refined minimalist
---

<section id="nosotros" class="py-32 px-6 sm:px-12 lg:px-16 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 lg:gap-32">
      <!-- Content -->
      <div>
        <p class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-white/40 mb-4">Sobre Nosotros</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem)] font-light tracking-[-0.02em] leading-[1.15] text-white mb-8">
          Facilitamos herramientas tecnológicas y educamos sobre su uso responsable.
        </h2>

        <p class="text-[15px] font-normal leading-[1.7] text-white/50 mb-16">
          No somos una empresa de software genérico ni vendemos soluciones enlatadas. 
          Diseñamos, construimos e implementamos herramientas digitales a medida, 
          pensadas para el contexto real de cada cliente.
        </p>

        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="space-y-10">
          <div class="group flex gap-6">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] text-blue-400/60 pt-1">01</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200">Negocios reales</h3>
              <p class="text-[14px] font-normal leading-[1.6] text-white/40">Trabajamos con negocios reales, no con casos de laboratorio.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group flex gap-6">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] text-blue-400/60 pt-1">02</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200">Lenguaje simple</h3>
              <p class="text-[14px] font-normal leading-[1.6] text-white/40">Explicamos todo en lenguaje simple, sin tecnicismos innecesarios.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group flex gap-6">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] text-blue-400/60 pt-1">03</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200">Soluciones duraderas</h3>
              <p class="text-[14px] font-normal leading-[1.6] text-white/40">Construimos cosas que duran y que el equipo puede usar sin depender de nosotros.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="group flex gap-6">
            <span class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] text-blue-400/60 pt-1">04</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-[16px] font-medium tracking-[-0.01em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-200">Impacto real</h3>
              <p class="text-[14px] font-normal leading-[1.6] text-white/40">Nos importa el impacto real en el negocio, no solo entregar código.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Stats -->
      <div class="lg:pt-16">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-white/10">
          <div class="bg-dark-900 p-8 sm:p-10 group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors duration-300">
            <p class="text-[40px] sm:text-[48px] font-light tracking-[-0.03em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">6</p>
            <p class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-white/40">Áreas de especialización</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-900 p-8 sm:p-10 group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors duration-300">
            <p class="text-[40px] sm:text-[48px] font-light tracking-[-0.03em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">9</p>
            <p class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-white/40">Servicios activos</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-900 p-8 sm:p-10 group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors duration-300">
            <p class="text-[40px] sm:text-[48px] font-light tracking-[-0.03em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">24/7</p>
            <p class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-white/40">Operación automática</p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-dark-900 p-8 sm:p-10 group hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors duration-300">
            <p class="text-[40px] sm:text-[48px] font-light tracking-[-0.03em] text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors duration-300">+35%</p>
            <p class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-white/40">Aumento ticket promedio</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Specializations list -->
        <div class="mt-12 pt-12 border-t border-white/10">
          <p class="text-[11px] font-normal tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-white/30 mb-6">Áreas de Especialización</p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p class="text-[14px] font-normal text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 cursor-default">Sistemas de fidelización</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] font-normal text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 cursor-default">Automatización de procesos</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] font-normal text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 cursor-default">Asistentes inteligentes</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] font-normal text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 cursor-default">Gestión de documentos</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] font-normal text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 cursor-default">Paneles de estadísticas</p>
            <p class="text-[14px] font-normal text-white/50 hover:text-white transition-colors duration-200 cursor-default">Generación de contenido</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
